rg-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweird%20%2414%20billion%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20buy%20just%20under%20half%20of%20Scale%20AI%20and%20its%20leader%2C%20Alex%20Wang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20ingredient%20required%20is%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20is%20tech%20jargon%20for%20the%20AI%20chips%20(GPUs%2C%20etc)%2C%20networking%20gear%2C%20and%20data%20centers%20needed%20to%20build%2C%20refine%2C%20and%20run%20giant%20AI%20models%20such%20as%20the%20Llama%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20SemiAnalysis%20blew%20the%20lid%20off%20Zuck's%20big%20plans%20for%20Meta's%20huge%20new%20AI%20infrastructure.%20You%20can%20read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsemianalysis.com%2F2025%2F07%2F11%2Fmeta-superintelligence-leadership-compute-talent-and-data%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You'll%20need%20to%20pay%20to%20read%20the%20whole%20thing%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20serious%20about%20AI%2C%20you%20will%20prob%20want%20to%20shell%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuck%20confirmed%20some%20of%20the%20details%20of%20SemiAnalysis's%20report%20via%20a%20Facebook%20post%20on%20Monday.%20The%20CEO%20said%20Meta%20will%20build%20several%20new%20AI%20data%20centers%20that%20use%20more%20than%201%20gigawatt%20of%20power%20each.%20This%20is%20how%20data%20center%20capacity%20is%20measured%2C%20and%20anything%20in%20the%201%20gigawatt%20range%20is%20absolutely%20massive%20(or%20at%20least%20it%20was%20until%20now).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c3dbccb-f30a-4552-a671-6a658dad4129%5C%22%3EData%20centers%20in%20tents%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20that%20really%20caught%20my%20eye%20in%20the%20SemiAnalysis%20report%20is%20that%20Meta%20is%20building%20some%20of%20these%20AI%20data%20centers%20in%20tents%20right%20now.%20A%20Meta%20spokesperson%20confirmed%20this%2C%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20tents%20help%20the%20company%20add%20additional%20capacity%20to%20its%20data%20center%20campuses%20and%20stressed%20that%20the%20entire%20%26quot%3Bsupercluster%26quot%3B%20data%20center%20facility%20isn't%20just%20a%20tent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20good%2C%20because%20data%20centers%20house%20a%20lot%20of%20complex%2C%20expensive%20gear%20and%20this%20gear%20needs%20to%20be%20kept%20cool%20in%20really%20controlled%20ways%2C%20otherwise%20it%20might%20will%20overheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20building%20parts%20of%20data%20centers%20in%20tents%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20how%20quickly%20Zuck%20is%20moving%20to%20get%20additional%20AI%20compute%20capacity%20up%20and%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemember%20when%20Elon%20Musk%20had%20Tesla%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteslas-new-model-3-assembly-line-is-in-a-tent-2018-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaking%20Model%203%20cars%20in%20tents%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%20the%20company's%20Fremont%20factory%20in%202018%3F%20That%20was%20about%20speed%20to%20market%2C%20and%20Zuck%20is%20now%20doing%20this%20for%20data%20centers%20%E2%80%94%20likely%20taking%20a%20page%20from%20Elon's%20strategy%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInspired%20by%20xAI's%20unprecedented%20time-to-market%2C%20Meta%20is%20embracing%20a%20datacenter%20design%20that%20prioritizes%20speed%20above%20all%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Semianalysis%20wrote%20in%20their%20Friday%20report.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20already%20building%20more%20of%20them!%20Traditional%20datacenter%20and%20real%20estate%20investors%2C%20still%20somewhat%20reeling%20from%20xAI's%20Memphis%20site%20and%20time%20to%20market%2C%20will%20be%20shocked%20yet%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20prefabricated%20power%20and%20cooling%20modules%20to%20ultra-light%20structures%2C%20speed%20is%20of%20the%20essence%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETents%20get%20really%20hot%2C%20so%20this%20could%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20running%20the%20prefab%20parts%20of%20these%20AI%20data%20centers.%20Indeed%2C%20Semianalysis%20reported%20that%20Meta%20could%20shut%20down%20workloads%20during%20th