f%20the%20Executive%20Branch%2C%20has%20the%20ultimate%20authority%20to%20make%20decisions%20about%20staffing%20levels%2C%20administrative%20organization%2C%20and%20day-to-day%20operations%20of%20federal%20agencies%2C%26quot%3B%20Linda%20McMahon%2C%20Trump's%20education%20secretary%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20today's%20ruling%20is%20a%20significant%20win%20for%20students%20and%20families%2C%20it%20is%20a%20shame%20that%20the%20highest%20court%20in%20the%20land%20had%20to%20step%20in%20to%20allow%20President%20Trump%20to%20advance%20the%20reforms%20Americans%20elected%20him%20to%20deliver%20using%20the%20authorities%20granted%20to%20him%20by%20the%20U.S.%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sonia%20Sotomayor%20wrote%20in%20her%20dissent%20that%20the%20decision%20expedites%20%26quot%3Blawlessness%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20executive%20branch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20majority%20is%20either%20willfully%20blind%20to%20the%20implications%20of%20its%20ruling%20or%20naive%2C%20but%20either%20way%20the%20threat%20to%20our%20Constitution's%20separation%20of%20powers%20is%20grave%2C%26quot%3B%20Sotomayor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20this%20ruling%20means%20for%20the%20future%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20Signal%20at%20asheffey.97%2C%20or%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3