hat%20followed%20was%20less%20travel%20and%20more%20toil.%20In%20the%20kibbutz%20fields%20of%20Maagan%2C%20Harshit%20learned%20how%20to%20grow%20avocados%20directly%20from%20Israeli%20farmers%2C%20spending%20weeks%20understanding%20grafting%2C%20irrigation%2C%20pruning%2C%20and%20soil%20health.%20His%20mentor%2C%20Benny%20Weiss%2C%20taught%20him%20not%20just%20technique%20but%20a%20mindset%20%E2%80%94%20precision%2C%20documentation%2C%20and%20deep%20respect%20for%20local%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESowing%20in%20barren%20soil%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20India%2C%20Harshit%20had%20no%20readymade%20orchard%20waiting.%20He%20took%20five%20acres%20of%20family-owned%20barren%20land%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bhopal%20and%20began%20transforming%20it.%20He%20spent%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20on%20soil%20development%2C%20water-efficient%20drip%20systems%2C%20greenhouses%2C%20and%20setting%20up%20a%20nursery.%20His%20goal%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F458517%2Fhow-to-grow-avocados-at-home-farmers-share-step-by-step-guide-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejust%20to%20grow%20avocados%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20to%20build%20a%20scalable%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20red%20tape%20stood%20in%20the%20way.%20Importing%20saplings%20from%20Israel%20required%20multiple%20permissions%2C%20quarantine%20protocols%2C%20and%20paperwork%20that%20dragged%20on%20for%20months.%20Then%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20waiting%20in%20frustration%2C%20Harshit%20used%20this%20time%20to%20educate.%20He%20launched%20a%20blog%2C%20wrote%20a%20free%20e-book%20on%20avocado%20farming%2C%20and%20began%20sharing%20his%20knowledge%20on%20YouTube%20and%20LinkedIn.%20Hundreds%20of%20aspiring%20farmers%20began%20writing%20to%20him.%20A%20quiet%20community%20was%20forming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20first%20saplings%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20nearly%20three%20years%20after%20he%20began%20the%20journey%2C%20Harshit%20finally%20received%20his%20first%20batch%20of%201%2C800%20Israeli%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F389465%2Fparmeshwar-thorat-avocado-organic-farming-drought-beed-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavocado%20saplings%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20planted%20five%20varieties%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Hass%2C%20Pinkerton%2C%20Ettinger%2C%20and%20Lamb-Hass%20%E2%80%94%20in%20raised%20beds%20enriched%20with%20compost%20and%20organic%20inputs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1752270202.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harshit%20began%20his%20journey%20on%20five%20acres%20of%20barren%20land%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bhopal.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1752270202.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1752270202-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1752270202-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1752270202-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-1_11zon-1752270202-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468499%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarshit%20began%20his%20journey%20on%20five%20acres%20of%20barren%20land%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bhopal.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20grow%20for%20himself.%20His%20Bhopal-based%20venture%2C%20Indo%20Israel%20Avocado%2C%20soon%20became%20a%20hub%20for%20sapling%20distribution%20and%20agro-consulting.%20Harshit%20supplied%20plants%20to%20farmers%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Assam%2C%20and%20even%20Sikkim.%20His%20model%20also%20offered%20a%20buyback%20option%20%E2%80%94%20farmers%20could%20sell%20their%20produce%20back%20to%20his%20network%2C%20reducing%20risk%20and%20market%20anxiety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20manages%20over%2020%2C000%20avocado%20plants%2C%20trains%20farmers%2C%20and%20works%20with%20luxury%20hotels%2C%20boutique%20stores%2C%20and%20chefs%20looking%20for%20locally%20grown%2C%20high-quality%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20passion%20into%20prosperity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202023%2C%20Indo%20Israel%20Avocado%20had%20clocked%20over%20Rs%201%20crore%20in%20revenue.%20But%20for%20Harshit%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20the%20money.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20goal%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20to%20grow%20avocados%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20to%20make%20%E2%80%98Sourced%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20a%20reality%20on%20every%20label.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%E2%80%99s%20also%20building%20a%20knowledge%20bank%20%E2%80%94%20every%20drop%20of%20water%2C%20every%20pruning%20schedule%2C%20every%20pest%20management%20technique%20is%20documented.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20other%20farmers%20to%20have%20the%20kind%20of%20detailed%20guidance%20I%20had%20to%20fly%20across%20the%20world%20to%20get%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENot%20just%20farming%2C%20but%20a%20movement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20country%20where%20avocados%20are%20still%20mostly%20imported%20%E2%80%94%20and%20often%20considered%20elite%20%E2%80%94%20Harshit%20is%20changing%20perceptions.%20His%20model%20is%20sustainable%2C%20low-water%2C%20and%20tailored%20for%20Indian%20conditions.%20His%20farm%20uses