scinated%20me%20from%20the%20moment%20I%20first%20heard%20about%20it%2C%20and%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20Instagram%20algorithm%2C%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20Neil%20%26amp%3B%20Momo%E2%80%99s%20page%20while%20searching%20for%20sustainability%20content.%20I%20have%20been%20following%20them%20since%20the%20very%20beginning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20finally%20made%20it%20to%20their%20March%20workshop%2C%20and%20it%20felt%20like%20stepping%20into%20a%20space%20I%20had%20been%20searching%20for.%20The%20experience%20was%20full%20of%20insight%20on%20sustainable%20practices%20and%20the%20people%20were%20curious%2C%20kind%2C%20and%20had%20similar%20thought%20processes%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20even%20more%20special.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20memorable%20moments%20for%20me%20was%20learning%20about%20how%20roots%20connect%20underground%20and%20how%20soil%20functions%20much%20like%20the%20human%20body.%20As%20someone%20trained%20in%20homoeopathy%2C%20that%20parallel%20was%20incredibly%20exciting.%20And%20yes%2C%20I%20dug%20my%20hands%20into%20cow%20dung%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20absolutely%20loved%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20impactful%20moments%20during%20the%20workshop%20was%20a%20life%20cycle%20analysis%20(LCA)%20activity%2C%20which%20revealed%20the%20hidden%20environmental%20cost%20of%20everyday%20consumer%20habits.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20really%20hit%20me%2C%20I%20uninstalled%20all%20my%20e-commerce%20apps%20while%20still%20on%20the%20farm%2C%20and%20have%20not%20felt%20the%20urge%20to%20go%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGoodbye%20apps%2C%20hello%20conscious%20living%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20workshop%2C%20Srushti%20has%20begun%20planning%20a%20green%20space%20of%20her%20own%2C%20with%20native%20trees%2C%20birds%2C%20and%20a%20small%20food-growing%20area.%20A%20chance%20connection%20with%20a%20native%20plant%20expert%20at%20the%20farm%20helped%20her%20finally%20convince%20her%20parents%20that%20native%20plants%20can%20be%20beautiful%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamika%20Bhide%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20playback%20singer%20based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20attended%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F424318%2Ffive-farm-volunteering-opportunities-in-tamil-nadu-auroville-chennai-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epermaculture%20workshop%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20her%20husband%20after%20watching%20one%20of%20Neil%20%26amp%3B%20Momo%E2%80%99s%20interviews%20online.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20been%20following%20them%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20that%20interview%20really%20struck%20a%20chord%3B%20we%20did%20not%20just%20want%20to%20admire%20what%20they%20were%20doing%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20understand%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205157.563_11zon-1752247338.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20workshops%20cost%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20participant%2C%20covering%20all%20sessions%2C%20materials%2C%20site%20visits%2C%20and%20meals%20made%20from%20farm-fresh%20ingredients%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205157.563_11zon-1752247338.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205157.563_11zon-1752247338-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205157.563_11zon-1752247338-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205157.563_11zon-1752247338-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205157.563_11zon-1752247338-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-468408%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20workshops%20cost%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20participant%2C%20covering%20all%20sessions%2C%20materials%2C%20site%20visits%2C%20and%20meals%20made%20from%20farm-fresh%20ingredients%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20factor%20that%20resonated%20most%20with%20her%20was%20how%20integrated%20the%20learning%20was.%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20we%20discussed%20in%20the%20theory%20sessions%20was%20already%20alive%20and%20implemented%20on%20the%20farm.%20It%20was%20not%20abstract%3B%20it%20was%20right%20there%20in%20front%20of%20us.%20The%20farm%20tour%20made%20everything%20click.%20We%20finally%20understood%20what%20it%20means%20to%20design%20with%20nature%2C%20not%20against%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20that%20clarity%20began%20to%20shift%20their%20everyday%20choices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20stopped%20relying%20on%20delivery%20apps%20and%20began%20sourcing%20our%20food%20from%20local%20farmers%E2%80%99%20markets.%20We%20also%20replaced%20chemical-heavy%20products%20with%20natural%20alternatives%20and%20even%20started%20a%20small%20kitchen%20garden%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workshop%20gave%20them%20the%20confidence%20to%20think%20long-term.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20now%20seriously%20considering%20buying%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20where%20we%20can%20apply%20these%20principles.%20We%20have%20also%20started%20talking%20to%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20about%20sustainability%2C%20not%20by%20preaching%2C%20just%20by%20sharing%20what%20has%20changed%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Shamika%2C%20the%20biggest%20realisation%20was%2C%20%E2%80%9CPermaculture%20is%20not%20only%20about%20growing%20food%2C%20it%20is%20a%20mindset.%20It%20is%20a%20lens%20through%20which%20you%20can%20reimagine%20how%20you%20live%2C%20what%20you%20consume%2C%20and%20how%20you%20connect%20with%20the%20world%20around%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReal%20changes%20take%20place%20slowly%20and%20steadily%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20Neil%20%26amp%3B%20Momo%20is%20also%20one%20of%20measurable%20environmental%20success.%20When%20they%20first%20arrived%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Mahabaleshwar%2C%20the%20earth%20beneath%20their%20feet%20was%20dry%2C%20compacted%2C%20and%20stripped%20of%20life.%20The%20topsoil%20had%20eroded%20from%20years%20of%20conventional%20agriculture%2C%20and%20very%20little%20could%20grow%20without%20heavy%20chemical%20inputs.%20But%20rather%20than%20turn%20away%2C%20they%20saw%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205519.042_11zon-1752247547.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20helps%20people%20understand%20how%20they%20can%20also%20start%20living%20a%20zero-waste%20life%20in%20the%20city%20by%20making%20small%20changes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205519.042_11zon-1752247547.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-11T205519.042_11zon-1752247547-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett