hutters%2C%20the%20wheels%20are%20chugging%2024%C3%977.%20The%20Elloras%20kitchen%20is%20a%20hive%20of%20activity%3B%20time%20is%20no%20constraint.%20Drona%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20always%20felt%20that%20bakery%20items%20are%20morning%20items%20and%20should%20be%20served%20fresh.%20So%20we%20plan%20in%20a%20way%20that%20our%20production%20continues%20throughout%20the%20night%20so%20that%20when%20we%20open%20our%20outlets%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20everything%20is%20fresh.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20clientele%20at%20Elloras%20is%20proof%20that%20their%20dedication%20is%20paying%20off.%20Among%20those%20who%E2%80%99ve%20stopped%20by%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F267757%2Fkapil-dev-world-cup-indian-cricket-captain-success-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eveteran%20cricketers%20Kapil%20Dev%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20chef%20Sanjeev%20Kapoor%2C%20the%20Kapoor%20family%2C%20the%20Gandhi%20family%2C%20chief%20ministers%2C%20and%20even%20the%20Maharani%20of%20Patiala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharani%20visited%20when%20senior%20Gulati%20was%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20things%2C%20in%20the%20bakery%E2%80%99s%20nascent%20days.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20there%20used%20to%20be%20a%20shortage%20of%20Coca-Cola%3B%20you%20had%20to%20book%20in%20advance%20if%20you%20had%20a%20wedding%20in%20the%20house.%20The%20Maharani%20of%20Patiala%20had%20been%20travelling%20along%20the%20Dehradun%20highway%20and%20observed%20that%20Coca-Cola%20was%20being%20sold%20at%20a%20premium%20everywhere.%20Only%20at%20our%20store%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20buy%20it%20at%20MRP%2C%20because%20my%20grandfather%20did%20not%20believe%20in%20raising%20the%20price%20of%20any%20item.%E2%80%9D%20Drona%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CShe%20was%20very%20impressed%20by%20his%20honesty.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20this%20he%20says%2C%20is%20what%20El