07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-74-1752147602.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-74-1752147602-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-74-1752147602-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-74-1752147602-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-74-1752147602-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467293%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3ENo%20one%20in%20Beed%20believed%20that%20avocado%20farming%20could%20succeed%2C%20but%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20perseverance%20paid%20off%20in%202021%20when%20his%2050%20plants%20began%20to%20produce%20fruit!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20starting%20avocado%20farming%20in%20Beed%20was%20far%20from%20easy.%20The%20region%20being%20notorious%20for%20its%20extreme%20temperatures%20and%20chronic%20water%20scarcity%2C%20the%20challenges%20initially%20seemed%20insurmountable%20for%20cultivating%20avocados.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20very%20little%20knowledge%20about%20avocado%20farming%20here%2C%20and%20no%20one%20had%20attempted%20it%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parmeshwar%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20overcome%20these%20challenges%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20did%20was%20dig%20two%20feet%20by%20two%20feet%20pits%20across%200.75%20acres%20of%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%20filled%20them%20with%20cow%20dung%20manure%20before%20planting%20the%20saplings.%20I%20knew%20the%20soil%20needed%20enrichment%20to%20supply%20the%20nutrients%20the%20plants%20required.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20he%20installed%20a%20drip%20irrigation%20system%20to%20ensure%20the%20saplings%20received%20adequate%20water%20without%20wastage.%20%E2%80%9CDrip%20irrigation%20takes%20water%20and%20other%20nutrients%20directly%20to%20the%20roots%2C%20minimising%20wastage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%20also%20utilised%20a%20pond%20on%20his%20farm%20to%20capture%20rainwater%20runoff.%20The%20stored%20water%20is%20used%20during%20the%20dry%20months%20of%20March%20and%20April%2C%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20groundwater.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20collect%20as%20much%20rainwater%20as%20possible%20during%20the%20monsoon%20and%20use%20it%20during%20the%20dry%20seasons.%20It%20helps%20keep%20the%20farm%20sustainable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20careful%20planning%20bore%20fruit%20when%20the%20first%20avocados%20were%20harvested%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20doubt%20to%20demand%3A%20Building%20a%20market%20for%20avocados%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20beginning%2C%20no%20one%20in%20Beed%20believed%20that%20avocado%20farming%20could%20succeed.%20But%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20perseverance%20paid%20off.%20By%202021%2C%20his%2050%20plants%20began%20to%20produce%20fruits!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20by%202022%2C%20he%20sold%20his%20first%20batch%20for%20Rs%20200%20per%20fruit%2C%20earning%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20people%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20much%20about%20avocados%20in%20my%20region%2C%20but%20after%20I%20distributed%20samples%2C%20they%20became%20curious.%20Slowly%2C%20the%20demand%20started%20building%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20factors%20behind%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20his%20commitment%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386464%2Fcouples-organic-farming-business-sreshte-guntur-andhra-pradesh-turnover-90-lakh-per-year%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAvocados%20are%20a%20healthy%20fruit%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20keep%20them%20that%20way.%20Initially%2C%20I%20used%20chemical%20fertilisers%20and%20pesticides%2C%20but%20after%20learning%20about%20organic%20farming%2C%20I%20changed%20my%20techniques%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20cow%20dung%20manure%20and%20natural%20farming%20methods%20not%20only%20ensures%20the%20health%20of%20the%20plants%20but%20also%20appeals%20to%20consumers%20who%20are%20becoming%20more%20aware%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20organic%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESister%20Annie%2C%20an%20advocate%20of%20sustainable%20agriculture%2C%20has%20been%20a%20witness%20to%20his%20transformation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20visited%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20farm%20and%20observed%20his%20avocado%20cultivation%20practices.%20After%20recommending%20a%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming%2C%20the%20results%20were%20remarkable.%20The%20yield%20improved%20significantly%2C%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20fruit%20enhanced%2C%20and%20they%20stayed%20fresh%20for%20a%20week%20without%20refrigeration%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%20significantly%20increased%20his%20profits%20by%20incorporating%20grafting%20techniques%20into%20his%20farming%20approach.%20%E2%80%9CGrafting%20helps%20extend%20the%20lifespan%20of%20the%20plants%2C%20which%20will%20benefit%20future%20generations%20of%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-76-1752147850.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Parmeshwar%20uses%20cow%20dung%20manure%20and%20natural%20farming%20methods%20to%20keep%20his%20produce%20healthy%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-76-1752147850.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-76-1752147850-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-76-1752147850-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-76-1752147850-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-76-1752147850-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467296%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3EParmeshwar%20uses%20cow%20dung%20manure%20and%20natural%20farming%20methods%20to%20keep%20his%20produce%20healthy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrafting%20involves%20joining%20the%20roots%20of%20one%20plant%20(known%20as%20rootstock)%20with%20the%20shoot%20or%20sapling%20of%20another%20(called%20the%20scion).%20He%20sources%20the%20rootstock%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20uses%20scions%20from%20his%20existing%20plants.%20This%20technique%20not%20only%20improves%20the%20health%20of%20the%20plants%20but%20also%20enhances%20their%20yield%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrafting%20costs%20around%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20Parmeshwar%20grafted%20around%20250%20new%20saplings.%20These%20plants%20are%20expected%20to%20start%20fruiting%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20%E2%80%9CGrafting%20is%20a%20game-changer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20extends%20the%20lifespan%20of%20avocado%20plants%20and%20boosts%20their%20yield%20potential.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%2C%20a%2062-year-old%20retired%20postal%20employee%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20supporting%20Parmeshwar%20by%20supplying%20avocado%20plants%20for%20his%20farm.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20I%20come%20from%20a%20non-farming%20background%2C%20we%20both%20began%20this%20journey%20of%20avocado%20farming%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20Parmeshwar%20visited%20Karnataka%20to%20learn%20about%20avocado%20cultivation%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20Kannada%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20we%20met.%20I%20explained%20everything%20to%20him.%20His%20perseverance%20and%20dedication%20were%20clear%2C%20and%20over%20time%2C%20they%20helped%20him%20become%20a%20successful%20avocado%20farmer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20avocado%20saplings%20I%20planted%20have%20yet%20to%20bear%20fruit.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Parmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20thriving%2C%20and%20he%E2%80%99s%20now%20successfully%20harvesting%20avocados!%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELeading%20by%20example%3A%20Educating%20the%20next%20generation%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%E2%80%99s%20journey%20into%20avocado%20farming%20is%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-agriculture-solar-dryer-biofertiliser-tree-scooter-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremarkable%20story%20of%20innovation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20sustainable%20practices.%20What%20started%20with%20just%2050%20saplings%20on%20a%20small%20plot%20of%20land%20has%20now%20blossomed%20into%20a%20thriving%201.75-acre%20farm%20%E2%80%94%20home%20to%20300%20avocado%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20harvested%20and%20sold%20around%201%2C200%20kg%20of%20avocados%2C%20earning%20a%20profit%20of%20Rs%205-6%20lakh%20after%20selling%20each%20fruit%20at%20Rs%20200.%E2%80%9D%20He%20mentions%20that%20maintaining%20the%20farm%20costs%20him%20about%20Rs%2050%2C000%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20selling%20the%20fruit%2C%20he%20has%20also%20ventured%20into%20selling%20avocado%20saplings.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20sold%202%2C300%20saplings%20at%20Rs%20300%20each.%20After%20accounting%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20he%20claims%20to%20have%20made%20a%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%204.6%20lakh%20from%20sapling%20sales.%20In%20total%2C%20his%20net%20profit%20for%20the%20year%202023%20was%20approximately%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20per%20acre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Parmeshwar%20is%20determined%20to%20expand%20his%20business.%20%E2%80%9CI%20plan%20to%20supply%20my%20avocados%20to%20markets%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Mumbai%20next%20year%2C%20while%20continuing%20to%20sell%20in%20Beed%20and%20Pune%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Grafting%20costs%20around%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20Parmeshwar%20grafted%20around%20250%20new%20saplings.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-75_11zon-1752147727-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-467294%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGrafting%20costs%20around%20Rs%20100%20per%20sapling%2C%20and%20in%202022%2C%20Parmeshwar%20grafted%20around%20250%20new%20saplings.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEqually%20passionate%20about%20educating%20others%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20teach%20farmers%20how%20to%20grow%20avocados%20in%20drought-prone%20areas%20using%20drip%20irrigation%20and%20organic%20methods.%E2%80%9D%20Many%20farmers%20have%20already%20visited%20his%20farm%20to%20learn%20from%20his%20experience%2C%20and%20he%20is%20eager%20to%20share%20his%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmeshwar%20advises%20other%20farmers%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20want%20to%20earn%20profits%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20community%2C%20consider%20starting%20avocado%20farming.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20growing%20a%20profitable%20crop%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20cultivating%20something%20that%20is%20healthy%20and%20beneficial%20for%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20emphasises%20the%20importance%20of%20adaptability%20and%20perseverance%3A%20%E2%80%9CFarming%20is%20not%20easy.%20There%20will%20always%20be%20challenges%2C%20but%20with%20determination%20and%20a%20willingness%20to%20learn%2C%20you%20can%20overcome%20anything.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20buy%20the%20avocados%2C%20you%20can%20reach%20Parmeshwar%20at%207875185032.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%20Parmeshwar%20Thorat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1752150600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-74-1752147602.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D467246%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parmeshwar%20Thorat%20from%20Beed%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20turned%20the%20challenges%20of%20arid%20conditions%20and%20water%20scarcity%20into%20an%20opportunity%20by%20pioneering%20avocado%20farming.%20Despite%20the%20initial%20doubts%20and%20harsh%20environment%2C%20his%20innovative%20approach%20has%20transformed%20his%201.75-acre%20farm%20into%20a%20profitable%20venture%2C%20yielding%201%2C200%20kg%20of%20av